{"type": "article", "id": 32387, "title": "加上这个小方块，旧音响马上可以蓝牙｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-09-19T23:05:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 21013, "name": "Paul Cocksedge Studio"}, {"id": 32941, "name": "Studioilse"}, {"id": 32942, "name": "Grav Grav"}, {"id": 32943, "name": "Altered:"}, {"id": 32944, "name": "Zanat"}, {"id": 25158, "name": "Ola Giertz"}, {"id": 32945, "name": "Hakan Gürsu"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 132, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160920003229YHbILtEpycPs9KMl.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Altered:Nozzle by Altered:</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.alteredcompany.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Altered:</a> 是一家瑞典的初创公司，它的三位创始人虽然来自不同行业但都非常关注水资源问题，自 2014 年 8 月他们就着手研发这款名为 Altered:Nozzle 的喷嘴，省水效果能够达到 98%。和其他需要整组更换的喷嘴不同，它可以直接安装在现有的龙头上。水经过喷嘴后将雾化成高速运动的微小水珠，增加了与其它物体的接触面积，相当于只用原水量的 2% 就能达到日常清洗的效果。除了省水 98% 的模式之外，喷嘴还有一个省水 75% 的普通模式，只要左右转动就能切换，方便人们蓄水。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/621008351/altered-nozzle-same-tap-98-less-water\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 374 瑞典克朗。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609200034363WeuGANUDrV4pPRO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003436F2BJQCExO7UKw9pZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.970588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003437GtPl8p3VyZiDca9d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609200034350qhNJ9VvIEW7nfCz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003435nIKBJd86ysk2zeCo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.795588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609200034359wdZ7bXD8yqCcBKr.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.520588\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Mr. T by Ola Giertz</h3><p>在研究了各种字体之后，瑞典设计师 <a href=\"http://olagiertz.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ola Giertz</a> 最终选择以字母 T 为原型打造了这张名为 <a href=\"http://olagiertz.se/pearllight/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mr. T</a> 的极简坐凳。它由垂直和水平的两个管状结构组合而成，笔直的字体轮廓和圆形截面形成了鲜明的对比，外形简单又不失趣味。Mr. T 的底座配有转轴方便人们随意调整就坐的方向，很适合放在开放式的空间，能够创造出更加灵活轻松的交流环境。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016092000345898hdfPKJY5lSamy2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.834963\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003458bRhti6oqINeZ0nY7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003458w8hKIHNPeQc5YEtW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.834963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003458n4g7oTZxfNXbWHQ1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003458ntjUCwiIRSFZm97Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.724939\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Touch Collection by Zanat &amp; Studioilse</h3><p>如果你钟情于木料独特的触感，英国 <a href=\"http://www.studioilse.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studioilse</a> 工作室在巴黎家居装饰博览会秋展上展出的这套 Touch 系列家具会让你忍不住伸手摸上去。这套家具包括了长凳、托盘和灯桌，表面奇妙的纹理由制造商 <a href=\"http://www.zanat.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Zanat</a> 的工匠选用实木手工雕刻而成。每件家具的雕刻需要两位工匠协作一天才能完成，期间工匠并不会参考任何草图，因此每一件家具都是独一无二的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003403wjD3RUo50lKIdWXH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003401N4wXfGcM5JgmnYiQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003402TQNwHpRIkusJj9F6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.704156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003404aDo0HTg8teNAKb2U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.416667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609200034011rFOuRh7scHzVK20.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003403mVbqweE31so2X0Iu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Reverence by Hakan Gürsu</h3><p>由 <a href=\"http://hakangursu.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hakan Gürsu</a> 设计的这款弯着腰的茶壶 <a href=\"https://competition.adesignaward.com/design.php?ID=44946\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reverence</a> 是不是会让你联想到侍者恭敬地为客人倒茶的模样？构成这一吸睛外形的其实是上下一小一大两个独立的茶壶，上层用来盛茶的小玻璃壶底部和不透明的大热水壶顶部刚好完美地契合在一起，塑造出背部优雅的曲线。热水壶采用珍珠岩作为隔热材质，不仅能为壶内的热水保温，还能向上提供热蒸气让茶水也能维持在一定温度。这项设计还获得了2016 年度 A’Design 设计大奖的肯定。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003337s3pq6U9HNM1iWJ4Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003337bpxIaLoKuzZUVDTv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003337tPLX5naQAiC7xISH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003337X23nJilfdLgz90PF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Cross Stitched Wood Bags &amp; Clutches by Grav Grav</h3><p><a href=\"https://gravgrav.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Grav Grav</a> 是一个由土耳其设计师 Merve Burma 创立的品牌，专门出售木制的手拿包和背包。除了别出心裁地选用木头作为原材料之外，Burma 还会制作动植物主题的刺绣点缀包面。精致的图案搭配温润的木头使整个设计充满了一股别致的自然气息，走在街上相当引人注目。这是它的<a href=\"http://gravgrav.com/collections/wooden-purse-clutch\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价从 199 到 880 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609200033234rn3mEcAo7LTbKjF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667692\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003323VJzTZinwI1spLa2R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003323VYWIsG5Twr8u6Dml.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.195652\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003323ZcqIbofVzOSK1nNP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.266667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003323J48I36aOQzFbsD5L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.266667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003324XJUewSsvMcNB8KbV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.195556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Vamp Stereo + Speaker by Paul Cocksedge Studio</h3><p>随着蓝牙音响的普及，你可能已经不太会再使用家中那些老旧且不具备蓝牙功能的音响了。来自英国的 Paul Cocksedge 工作室最近推出了一款名为 Vamp 的小装置，帮助那些充满回忆的旧物以另一种方式重新回到我们的日常生活中。和我们之前介绍的那些<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/31759.html\">废物利用</a>不同，Vamp 本身并不对旧音响进行改造，而是充当了桥梁的作用：它本身是一个造型独特的立方体，内置蓝牙芯片、放大器和充电电池，背部则集成了一些老式的音频线缆接口。通过线缆将 Vamp 和旧音响连接在一起后，不具备蓝牙功能的那些古董设备也能像蓝牙音响那样播放出手机上的音乐了。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1238747394/the-vamp-stereo-speaker-bring-back-the-sound\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 69 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003259FCln98OEGhjgvJ63.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003258neHEpsgWKGi5u7fy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003258pfyun0dSjO3EsBql.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.674817\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003300CDEQ6yvMBle25VaP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609200032599AThVDN5WswiCyHu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.470660\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920003259y0CGL86mIpaxbcjr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}